T1  - ORGANIZATION-MOTIVATED AGGRESSION: A RESEARCH FRAMEWORK
AU  - O'Leary-Kelly, Anne M.
AU  - Griffin, Ricky W.
AU  - Glew, David J.
Y1  - 1996/01/01
PY  - 1996
